{
  "id": "RAW_3536dbd7",
  "title": "做 AI 眼镜，为何 Rokid 乐奇能成为大厂们的学习对象？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==&mid=2652793726&idx=1&sn=295ccb5bbb971025d7a65caec8cb1036",
  "date": "2025-12-04 11:02:00",
  "author": "智东西",
  "siteName": "智东西",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5bdc883b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricsXOyMicK2Q30teMKicKEMSBfODdD0nNXboH7dXFFPegWuHQkjpvxeQ2w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">巨头创企入场，AI眼镜暴卷，Rokid乐奇先一步找到破局之道。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">云鹏</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">漠影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">短短几周内，百度、阿里AI眼镜先后开卖，大厂入局之下，AI眼镜创企要如何求存，已经成为当前从业者和投资人都非常关心的话题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于大部分创业公司来讲，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">大厂下场，或为“死局”：营销、供应链、价格战“三板斧”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">带给创企的压力是显而易见的，局势并不乐观。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">面对死局，如何“破局”？</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">对于这一问题，差异化竞争、找到自身独特价值和优势是大部分创业者给出的答案。但究竟如何找准自身定位，做好充足准备应对冲击，并不是所有玩家都想清楚了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">就在最近，国内AI眼镜领域头部玩家Rokid乐奇与全球头部时尚眼镜品牌BOLON眼镜一起做了场科技与时尚结合的发布会，也真正让Rokid乐奇眼镜再次破圈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505310062\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.56171875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/z7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricS3EjevCvjYPHTUDZjkYCSkcibTIJfmCiaKkBTE083hD0kjjND37gt9sA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"239\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=549286af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricS3EjevCvjYPHTUDZjkYCSkcibTIJfmCiaKkBTE083hD0kjjND37gt9sA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">破圈之余，越来越多人开始注意到Rokid乐奇眼镜在产品功能细节上的用心打磨和产品体验上的极致“死磕”，经过多轮打磨迭代后，Rokid乐奇眼镜的实际体验可以说是</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“口碑爆棚”。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">用心倾听用户、专注打磨产品，已经成为人们对Rokid乐奇这家公司的普遍印象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">或许寻求“破局”的路既难又简单，难是因为要克服来自各方面的诸多挑战，说简单是因为只要在确定的方向上做到极致，自会展现出独特价值，得到市场和消费者认可。这或许正是</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Rokid乐奇的信心和底气所在。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">近期智东西深度体验了Rokid乐奇眼镜，在诸多产品设计细节中，磁吸式充电以及充电胶囊的设计给我们留下深刻印象，其背后包含了大量Rokid乐奇对用户体验的深入思考。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7527777777777778\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e9afa9a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricuAJ1bG49ic3y9LwjHnzzcY4oib6vicVeCM79uT4MnPqxFFqPXuiauVmibEw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲Rokid乐奇眼镜</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，从提词器、翻译、导航、拍照到AI问答，Rokid乐奇在诸多环节的细节优化都令人印象深刻，而这些丰富功能的实现，都需要出色续航底层能力的支撑，能量胶囊让这些功能真正“随时随地”可用，告别续航焦虑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">大厂入局之下，“小而美”的Rokid乐奇似乎已经找到了自己的清晰生存路径。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">首创磁吸式充电背后：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">4个版本迭代死磕体验细节</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">充电胶囊成行业方向</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI眼镜发展至今，性能和功耗的平衡仍然是核心难题之一，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">丰富的功能如果离开了强劲续航的支撑，就相当于无本之木，只能“昙花一现”，无法在消费者日常生活中真正变得常用。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，我们看到Rokid用户在拥有10万活跃用户、覆盖全球五大洲的社区大量分享自己的体验感受，可以说直接把AI眼镜的各种功能“玩出了花”：</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">第一视角笼中飞车惊险刺激、雪地翻飞动感十足、小语种翻译流畅高效，甚至还有用户带来了西伯利亚雪原沉浸式捕猎的第一视角视频。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0% 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-end;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 200%;overflow-x: hidden;max-width: 200% !important;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 50%;vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;width: 100%;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/z7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricFPuFAxyagZUuyoG3oscO3QnHlNURxysRsHhdDuhjZJGxfR4KSicbnZg/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"553\" data-cropsely2=\"553\" data-imgfileid=\"505310072\" data-ratio=\"1.3551020408163266\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"490\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c1ce83f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricFPuFAxyagZUuyoG3oscO3QnHlNURxysRsHhdDuhjZJGxfR4KSicbnZg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 50%;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;width: 100%;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505310073\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.360323886639676\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"494\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/z7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricTMCxA4MtaW5kyLcjXSaHRxtgQR7ibibdTB3Iz01QIwg6bKdibPFqacrkQ/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"553\" data-cropsely2=\"553\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e5c23c8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricTMCxA4MtaW5kyLcjXSaHRxtgQR7ibibdTB3Iz01QIwg6bKdibPFqacrkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: right;transform: translate3d(-27px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-27px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-27px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-27px, 0px, 0px);margin: 0px 0% 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(81, 81, 81);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">向右滑动查看更多</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.135135135135135\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" data-w=\"999\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1901ee7d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fric9DUqJffKJCUdgcoyicz6u3I5Ysp13Yx58jDynIkQjHThfksKxSl6uNQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲小语种翻译，来源：Rokid社区用户</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而一切这些“玩出花”的功能，都需要出色续航能力的保障。续航是AI眼镜的根本基础能力，对使用体验可以说是</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">“牵一发动全身”，</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">也是Rokid乐奇瞄准的重点优化方向之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了提升用户的充电和续航体验，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Rokid乐奇行业首创了AI眼镜磁吸式充电+充电胶囊的设计，</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">不少新入局的大厂也在沿袭Rokid乐奇的脚步，Rokid可以说给行业提供了一份优秀的标准答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7527777777777778\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ba6be68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricNUf6vbJFibbLR2s6bGfWXZWzI40XrtlicMbhE8C0o1WI4fS6l65SDQ9w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲充电盒与充电胶囊</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体来看，Rokid乐奇眼镜是如何做磁吸充电的，相比行业中其他厂商通常沿用“做手机”的思路，用一个成熟的Type-C口方案来解决，Rokid乐奇准确把握到了AI眼镜这类头部穿戴设备对磁吸式充电的独特需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在佩戴过程中，我可以随时单手快速插拔Rokid乐奇眼镜的磁吸式充电线，可以很好地适配边用边充场景，并且用户不用担心充电时被线材意外绊倒，伤害眼镜和用户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7868284228769498\" data-w=\"577\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f7eae45&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fric0fRLmHiaCnAh5DxEzpjFVriaknQaZqMgSYE23HvNGg90sDIW0ofoukVA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲遇到外力自动脱落避免损伤</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">此前苹果Vision Pro首发同样采用了磁吸式充电，后曾一度改为Type-C，但最后又用回磁吸，磁吸依然是穿戴设备充电的当前“最优解”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Rokid乐奇眼镜磁吸式充电带来的另一个显著优势就是可以搭配外置电池，彻底解决续航焦虑问题。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-b