px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个小小的磁吸式充电功能的打磨，让我们看到Rokid乐奇对产品体验的专注和死磕，其实这样的思路在Rokid乐奇产品中是一以贯之的，相比大厂的“水桶机”追求大而全，Rokid乐奇给自己的定位很清楚，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">先把核心的重点能力做到极致，让用户体验到位，不求大而全，而是将“小而美”做到极致。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.2\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3f926801&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricFoCOwUqNr5jESibBgP0x2NUJByhoYqmsuewvINmNvulKCg4icvuNH5lQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲Rokid乐奇眼镜核心能力</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如在轻量化和舒适佩戴方面，好的AI眼镜首先得是个好眼镜，为此Rokid乐奇优化了结构和重量分配，还专门设计了可拆卸鼻托，可以适配各种鼻型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6620370370370371\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd01aecd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricCzWkLgTQ3AsZBrw1wYdaOmAqEkzNLQHPiaK9GhibHe1Fknnhe4H1EbaQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲Rokid乐奇眼镜可拆卸鼻托</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">据了解，Rokid乐奇根据亚洲人脸大数据模型进行了数百次设计优化与细节打磨，进一步提升佩戴舒适度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">在拍照方面，</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">主流AI眼镜当前硬件同质化明显，供应链尚不成熟，尚无更多适配方案，因此软件算法深度优化就成为Rokid乐奇寻找差异化优势的关键。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Rokid乐奇通过HDR夜景增强让画面暗部更清晰生动，通过智能HDR让逆光场景的动态范围表现更好，暗光清晰度、画面动态范围。此外，Rokid乐奇还优化了视频多场景的色彩、曝光、运动模糊、室外清晰度等问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">值得一提的是，在视频拍摄方面，Rokid乐奇提供了3:4、9:16、4:3等各种比例可选，录制时长也新增了15秒、30秒、2分钟、5分钟，拍摄更自由。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以说，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Rokid乐奇让AI眼镜从“能拍到”向“拍的好”迈了一大步。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于Rokid乐奇眼镜“出圈”的</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">提词器</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">功能，Rokid乐奇支持了无极自定义调节，用户可以自由调整提词器和翻译的显示范围和显示高度，提词器的字号也可以调整。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3365384615384615\" data-w=\"416\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dede48bb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricUG5CdQPwGTIzqJ85hWYdS2H8BUcX1xJNG26kxnMuUR4ibQsDg0ic5okQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲提词器功能</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">实时翻译</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">功能方面，Rokid乐奇支持了“双向翻译”，打通双向沟通，同时支持语言数量增加到89种，翻译时效控制在1秒以内。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8413461538461539\" data-w=\"416\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0c2117d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricYHb3zkZFGxRiaBP3gSOibwwkNLQj7S2lQyPWnicFByJrPPAxLlzz5XV7A%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲实时翻译延迟极低，准确率较高</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从实际体验来看，Rokid乐奇眼镜翻译的时延和准确率都不错，比如我们看一些无字幕的外文新闻播报或电影，这一功能都十分便捷好用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">支付</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">能力方面，“看一下支付”可以说给AI眼镜走入日常生活提供了一项核心基础能力，解放双手支付能在诸多场景中提供极高便捷性。比如当我开车出停车场时，就不需要把手机从支架上拿起，只需要看一下，既快捷又安全。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5435185185185185\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e262ece5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgvPBMQbIGlzsTibra4M7fricnE0qP4Oojv1vHd1Vyh42yQznw950GvnicLwicPP3C4Zld5ibI5QSmAb8w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可以说，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">从诸多Rokid乐奇对于产品细节的极致追求中，我们都能看到这家公司对于“小而美”的诠释。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Rokid乐奇深入用户实际使用场景，去洞察在每一个使用的环节可能存在哪些细节问题，Rokid乐奇要的不是“能用”，而是要“好用”。解决关键环节体验痛点，Rokid乐奇真正将一款精致的AR+AI眼镜和基于其实现的完善体验打包给到用户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：大厂入局搅动市场</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">创企小步快跑细节取胜</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今天，大厂入局AI眼镜赛道已经是确定趋势，更多玩家的加入，必然会带动市场快速起量，快速增长的市场规模也会进一步带动供应链的成熟，AI眼镜市场整体发展向好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">于此同时，行业竞争也会更加激烈，创企如何找准自身定位，形成差异化优势，十分重要。Rokid乐奇可以说给出了很好的范例模板：</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">把功夫花在刀刃上、不追求大而全，而是将细节体验、核心能力打磨到极致，形成口碑优势，与大厂产品形成差异化优势。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">就在今天下午，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rokid乐奇创始人兼CEO Misa刚刚剧透，他们将在年底迎来一次软件系统“大升级”，会有一个“神秘功能”，</span>或许会对行业有启发，感兴趣的朋友可以视频号搜索「Rokid乐奇」预约直播。不得不说，AI眼镜行业的充分竞争，正带给消费者越来越多的惊喜。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
